375
01:13:56.656 --> 01:14:04.966
Incoming livestream: Product-facing security, where as agents are doing more and more work on behalf of humans,


376
01:14:04.966 --> 01:14:16.836
Incoming livestream: a lot of the security landscape is changing, and so, like, what does identity look like? What does threat detection look like? And what does DLP look like? I think that's gonna significantly change in the next couple years.


377
01:14:17.206 --> 01:14:34.875
